OL,3,CCall for safer driving after
OL,4,C'catastrophic' weekend on NI roads
OL,6,FA joint Stormont and police call has
OL,7,Fbeen made for safer driving following
OL,8,Fa "catastrophic" weekend on Northern
OL,9,FIreland's roads.
OL,11,FFive people lost their lives on the
OL,12,Froads at the weekend.
OL,14,FIt brought the toll for the year so
OL,15,Ffar to 29, double the number for the
OL,16,Fsame period in 2015 when 14 fatalities
OL,17,Fhad been recorded.
OL,26,@pD@COUpD@PO]
