OL,3,CCall for safer driving after
OL,4,C'catastrophic' weekend on NI roads
OL,6,FSpeaking ahead of the bank holiday
OL,7,Fweekend, Infrastructure Minister Liz
OL,8,FKimmins and Assistant Chief Constable
OL,9,FMelanie Jones made a joint safety
OL,10,Fappeal.
OL,12,FMs Kimmins told a press conference at
OL,13,FPSNI headquarters in east Belfast they
OL,14,Fwere making the appeal "in the wake of
OL,15,Fwhat has been a horrendous weekend on
OL,16,Four roads".
OL,26,@vD@XOUxD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1777539988
OL,3,CCall for safer driving after
OL,4,C'catastrophic' weekend on NI roads
OL,6,F"A weekend which has left families
OL,7,Fabsolutely shattered by the shock and
OL,8,Fthe grief of losing their loved one,
OL,9,Fwhile others are coming to terms with
OL,10,Fthe injuries that they have
OL,11,Fsustained," she said.
OL,13,F"We're just four months into 2026 and
OL,14,F29 people have died so far, 29 people
OL,15,Fhave lost their lives on their roads,
OL,16,F29 people who set off on an every day
OL,17,Fjourney which turned out to be their
OL,18,Flast journey and last day.
OL,20,F"That means on average a life has been
OL,21,Flost every four days.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@KO]uD@AOU|D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1777539988
OL,3,CCall for safer driving after
OL,4,C'catastrophic' weekend on NI roads
OL,6,F"As we head into the bank holiday
OL,7,Fweekend, my appeal is for everyone to
OL,8,Ftake extra care, to control your
OL,9,Fspeed, to put your phone away, never
OL,10,Fever drink or take drugs and get
OL,11,Fbehind the wheel, don't get distracted
OL,12,Fand always wear your seatbelt."
OL,14,FMs Jones said the spike in road death
OL,15,Fnumbers comes after "some improvement"
OL,16,Fand a "slight decline" in recent years.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@_O]wD@UOUwD@fO]xD@GOUxD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1777539988
OL,3,CCall for safer driving after
OL,4,C'catastrophic' weekend on NI roads
OL,6,F"The past weekend has been
OL,7,Fcatastrophic on our roads, within 24
OL,8,Fhours, five people lost their lives in
OL,9,Ffour separate road traffic collisions,
OL,10,Fand other people received life
OL,11,Fchanging injuries," she said.
OL,13,F"These deaths are a stark and cruel
OL,14,Freminder of the very real dangers
OL,15,Fwhich exist on our roads.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@SO]uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1777539988
OL,3,CCall for safer driving after
OL,4,C'catastrophic' weekend on NI roads
OL,6,F"So far this year 29 people have lost
OL,7,Ftheir lives on the roads in Northern
OL,8,FIreland, that is the equivalent of a
OL,9,Fwhole classroom of students, this is
OL,10,F29 families whose lives have been
OL,11,Fchanged in an instant and forever,
OL,12,Ffriends and communities left
OL,13,Fdevastated.
OL,15,F"We're heading into another busy
OL,16,Fperiod on our roads, it's the first
OL,17,FMay bank holiday, and we have the
OL,18,FNorth West 200 in Portrush next week.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1777539988
OL,3,CCall for safer driving after
OL,4,C'catastrophic' weekend on NI roads
OL,6,F"Lots of people will be travelling to
OL,7,Fmeet family and friends, and spend
OL,8,Fsome downtime.
OL,10,F"My appeal is please be safe on our
OL,11,Froads.
OL,13,F"Societal attitudes on our roads need
OL,14,Fto change.
OL,16,F"All of these incidents are
OL,17,Fpreventable if we all take
OL,18,Fresponsibility for the choices we take
OL,19,Fon the roads."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUuD@AOUxD@AOU{D@NO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/9
