PN,44508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1777539988
OL,3,CCall for safer driving after
OL,4,C'catastrophic' weekend on NI roads
OL,6,FMs Jones said there will be a visible
OL,7,Fpolice presence on the roads this
OL,8,Fweekends, focusing on the "fatal
OL,9,Ffive", which include drink and drug
OL,10,Fdriving, speeding, excessive speed,
OL,11,Fuse of mobile phones, not wearing
OL,12,Fseatbelts and inattention and poor
OL,13,Fdecision making by drivers.
OL,15,F"If we all take personal
OL,16,Fresponsibility and do things a little
OL,17,Fdifferently on our roads, they will be
OL,18,Fa much safer place for everybody," she
OL,19,Fadded.
OL,26,@pD@[OUqD@EO]wD@AOUzD@bO]
